pretty easy to fix by removing the first argument for `useGroup` on this line (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/af5237c/webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/apps/src/aihub/pages/DeploymentStudio/ConfigureDeployment/HumanReview/ReviewQueues/ReviewQueueBase.tsx#L64), in case anyone encounters this

fyi @Jessica @Udit
ah, i'll quickly remove the line in that file!

i included the fix in my PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/61634), but it’s pretty big, so i expect it’ll take a while to merge :sweat:

a separate PR with just this fix would be great!
